import React from 'react'
import {Conatainer ,Logotip,Search,Store,LogoTitle,Logo} from './style'
const Navabr = () => {

        <Conatainer>

                 <Logo/>
                 <LogoTitle>Furniking</LogoTitle>

            <Search>salom</Search>

            <Store>xayir</Store>
        </Conatainer>
    )
}

export default Navabr
